snippet.title: Go-Go Town! - Official Couch Co-op Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: Go-Go Town!'s latest trailer reveals couch co-op play as you and your friends build and more in this upcoming life simulator game. Couch co-op for Go-Go Town is coming in February 2024. In Go-Go Town, as mayor, it’s up to you to breathe life back into this rundown town. Construct shops, hire staff, automate deliveries with couriers, and attract tourists to town, all while managing infrastructure and avoiding catastrophes. Who said being mayor was going to be easy?
